comments.message:
Hi Patrick, thanks a lot for the constructive comments! I will update the doc and upload a new version to respond to questions raised in the comments. Some design choices are still open for discussion. I shared my proposal in the comments and would like to hear your feedback.

@Ed Tanous, there is one question(comment at #130) raised in the comments that need your feedback, could you also help take a look?

Thanks!

Re Patrick:
Let me update the doc to make it clear that we need to create a repo for spdm daemon.

Re Ed:
This design has a section for spdm daemon. Regarding upstream sequence, I would propose the following one considering that the daemon has a dependency on the PDI changes:
1) new interfaces in PDI;
2) spdm daemon;
3) bmcweb changes;

I did started with the starter patchset 
https://gerrit.openbmc.org/c/openbmc/bmcweb/+/61702
thanks Ed!
